# Studio import path aliases (v2)

Consumers import **`@afenda/shadcn-studio-v2` package exports only** — never `packages/shadcn-studio-v2/src/*`.

## Two-layer model

| Layer | SSOT | Purpose | Example |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **Production (package)** | `packages/shadcn-studio-v2/tsconfig.json` | Internal `@/*` aliases for package source | `@/components/ui/button` → `src/components/ui/button.tsx` |
| **Consumer** | `package.json` exports | ERP / Storybook / developer imports | `@afenda/shadcn-studio-v2`, `@afenda/shadcn-studio-v2/clients` |

**Install cwd (MCP/CLI):** `packages/shadcn-studio-v2`

## Public exports

| Subpath | Consumer |
| --- | --- |
| `@afenda/shadcn-studio-v2` | Neutral surfaces, slot constants, server-safe types |
| `@afenda/shadcn-studio-v2/clients` | Client runtime (providers, hooks, composed views) |
| `@afenda/shadcn-studio-v2/shadcn-default.css` | Theme CSS (dist export) |
| `@afenda/shadcn-studio-v2/themes/*` | Scoped theme overlays |

## Forbidden

- `packages/shadcn-studio-v2/src/*` imports from `apps/erp`, `apps/storybook`, or `apps/developer`
- `@afenda/shadcn-studio` (v1 retired — use `pnpm check:v1-consumer-imports`)
- Legacy v1 paths: `components-ui/`, `components-quarantine/`, `components-layouts/`

## Symptom → fix

| Symptom | Likely cause | First check |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Consumer cannot resolve deep import | Deep src path used | Switch to package export subpath |
| IDE red squiggle on `@/` in consumer | Alias used outside package | Import from `@afenda/shadcn-studio-v2` barrel |
| Stale theme CSS at runtime | dist not synced | `pnpm sync:package-css-dist -- --package @afenda/shadcn-studio-v2` |

## Gates

```bash
pnpm check:v1-consumer-imports
pnpm check:downstream-integration
pnpm check:package-css-dist-sync
pnpm --filter @afenda/shadcn-studio-v2 typecheck
```

